HOW SUBSCRIPTIONS WORK
+
-
Subscribe to The Discovery Set to save £5 and try all five of AKT's signature Deodorant Balm fragrances.
After 30 days you will automatically be added to our standard subscription programme and be sent a full size SC.01 Orange Grove 50ml Deodorant Balm. You can change the fragrance you receive in your account at any time.
As a subscriber you will benefit from:
  • 15% off every full-size tube 💰
  • FREE UK delivery 📦
  • You can choose the frequency 📆
  • Easily swap or edit products/fragrances ✍🏼
  • Cancel your subscription anytime 🚫
If you wish to cancel your subscription after trying your mini deodorant balms you can do so in your account. Cancel within 29 days of your original purchase to avoid any recurring charges.

7 REASONS TO AKT

The top reasons why AKT scores 4.78/5 based on 21085 reviews

1. born to perform

Created and tested on dancers, not animals – to withstand 8 shows a week under hot stage lights. protection doesn’t get better than this.

2. NATURAL INGREDIENTS

Our proprietary formula uses a blend of clean, botanical and mineral ingredients to neutralise odours, cleanse the skin and keep you feeling dry all day.

3. PREMIUM FRAGRANCES

Premium fragrances inspired by scenes in nature. You've never had a deodorant that smells this amazing.


4. NO STAINS = NO DRAMA

Say goodbye to deodorant stains. AKT cares for your skin and your clothes, meaning your garments will last longer. Let's reduce fast fashion together.

5. GOOD FOR YOU & THE PLANET

AKT is 100% plastic free and recyclable. Even our bespoke aluminium caps!



6. GENDER FREE

AKT is for everyone! Our fragrances are unisex and designed for sensitive skin



7. MULTI-USE

AKT can be used anywhere you sweat — feet, forehead, chest. 1 tube lasts 6-8 weeks on average. Much longer than a supermarket deo — and a whole lot better.
